'''伯里'''（{{lang-en|Bury}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[大曼徹斯特郡|大曼徹斯特郡]]的一座[[城市|城市]]<ref name="GM Gazetteer">{{citation|url=http://www.gmcro.co.uk/Guides/Gazeteer/gazzb.htm|title=Greater Manchester Gazetteer|publisher=Greater Manchester County Record Office|accessdate=17 October 2008|at=Places names - B|archivedate=2011年7月18日|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718144414/http://www.gmcro.co.uk/Guides/Gazeteer/gazzb.htm|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，在歷史上曾屬於[[蘭開夏郡|蘭開夏郡]]。在工業革命時期伯里曾是一座工業都市<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=53012 |contribution=Townships: Bury |title=A History of the County of Lancaster: Volume 5 |year=1911 |pages=128–133 |editor=William Farrer & John Brownbill |series={{tsl|en|Victoria County History||Victoria County History}} |publisher=Constable |isbn=0-7129-1055-7 |access-date=2015-01-16 |archive-date=2014-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903075843/http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=53012 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伯里現在以其的露天市場[[伯里市場|伯里市場]]而聞名<ref>{{cite book |title=Bygone Bury |url=https://archive.org/details/cu31924028093726 |first=John |last=Lord |location=Rochdale |publisher=James Clegg, Aldine Press |year=1903}}</ref>，是曼彻斯特有轨电车系统的终点站。英国工业革命初期飞梭的发明人[[约翰·凯|约翰·凯]]是在这里出生的。

